A set of Vim configurations to use specially with Rails + Git

-- to set up the .vimrc file, use this command to create a symbolic link
ln -s vimrc ~/.vimrc
ln -s gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Needs:
- ctags               (>= 5.8)  http://ctags.sourceforge.net/

Have:
